'''Breakfast fruit''' was a common breakfast food on [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Factory world/Legends|factory worlds]] such as [[Metalorn/Legends|Metalorn]]. [[Tammia Hollusen]] planted seeds of breakfast fruit in an unapproved attempt to grow her own garden on the bleak [[Planet/Legends|planet]].

